'''時代公司'''（{{lang-en|Time Inc.}}）是曾经位于美国纽约的一间出版公司，其負責出版的雜誌有130多種<ref>[http://timewarner.com/corp/businesses/detail/time_inc/ Time Warner: Time Inc<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080723143812/http://timewarner.com/corp/businesses/detail/time_inc/ |date=2008-07-23 }}</ref>， 最著名者為《[[時代_(雜誌)|時代]]》、《[[生活_(雜誌)|生活]]》、《[[運動畫刊|運動畫刊]]》及《[[財星_(雜誌)|財星]]》。2017年11月，{{link-en|梅雷迪斯公司|Meredith Corporation}}宣布将以28亿美元的价格收购该公司；次年1月31日交易完成。<ref name="meredithpr">{{cite press release |url=http://meredith.mediaroom.com/index.php?s=2311&item=137161 |title=Meredith Corporation Announces Completion Of Time Inc. Acquisition And Reports Fiscal 2018 Second Quarter And First Half Results |date=January 31, 2018 |publisher=Meredith Corporation |accessdate=February 10, 2018 |archive-date=2018-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180204084323/http://meredith.mediaroom.com/index.php?s=2311&item=137161 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="wwd">{{cite journal |url=http://wwd.com/business-news/media/time-inc-first-day-meredith-corp-more-changes-to-come-11134819/ |title=Time Inc., Now Meredith and More Changes to Come |date=February 1, 2018 |last=Hays |first=Kali |journal=[[Women's_Wear_Daily|Women's Wear Daily]] |accessdate=February 10, 2018 |archive-date=2018-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180208164733/http://wwd.com/business-news/media/time-inc-first-day-meredith-corp-more-changes-to-come-11134819/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==历史==
1990年，時代公司和[[華納傳播|華納傳播]]合併而成[[時代華納|時代華納]]。2013年6月，時代華納宣佈，計劃將時代公司拆分出來變成[[上市公司|上市公司]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.ithome.com.tw/node/79126|title=時代華納宣布將拆分獨立Time Inc雜誌業務|author=陳曉莉|date=2013-03-07|work=|publisher=電週文化|newspaper=iThome|accessdate=2018-01-01|archive-date=2021-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210223055235/https://www.ithome.com.tw/node/79126|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | last = Lieberman | first = David, Financial Editor | url = http://www.deadline.com/2013/03/time-warner-publishing-magazines-spin-off/ | title = Time Warner plans to spin off Time Inc | publisher = [[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] | date = 6 March 2013 | accessdate = 20 April 2013 | archive-date = 2014-03-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140310112719/http://www.deadline.com/2013/03/time-warner-publishing-magazines-spin-off/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2013年10月1日，時代華納買下[[美國運通出版公司|美國運通出版公司]]的數個品牌，如《Travel + Leisure》、《Food & Wine》、《Departures》、《Black Ink》及《Executive Travel》<ref>{{cite web|title=Media It's Official: Time Inc. Buys AmEx's Food & Wine, Travel & Leisure Magazines|url=http://adage.com/article/media/time-buys-amex-s-food-wine-travel-leisure/244065/|work=Ad Age|publisher=Crain Communications|accessdate=11 October 2013|archive-date=2013-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012104625/http://adage.com/article/media/time-buys-amex-s-food-wine-travel-leisure/244065/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年6月9日，时代公司完成分离，成为一家独立的上市公司<ref name="twx">{{cite news|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/06/time-inc-and-time-warner-shares-slip-as-magazine-company-goes-public/|title=Time Inc Shares Slip As Magazine Company Goes Public|last=Lieberman|first=David|date=2014-06-09|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|publisher=[[Penske_Media_Corporation|Penske Media Corporation]]|accessdate=2014-07-28|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714213718/http://www.deadline.com/2014/06/time-inc-and-time-warner-shares-slip-as-magazine-company-goes-public/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年併購了社群網站[[Myspace|Myspace]]的母公司。

2017年11月25日，{{link-en|梅雷迪斯公司|Meredith Corporation}}宣佈以約28億美元併購時代公司<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/11/26/business/dealbook/time-inc-meredith-corporation-koch-brothers.html|title=Time Inc. Sells Itself to Meredith Corp., Backed by Koch Brothers|last1=Ember|first1=Sydney|date=2017-11-26|work=|last2=Sorkin|first2=Andrew Ross|newspaper=The New York Times|accessdate=2018-01-01|language=en-US|archive-date=2017-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171126222514/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/11/26/business/dealbook/time-inc-meredith-corporation-koch-brothers.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://tw.appledaily.com/international/daily/20171128/37858082|title=時代840億賣給梅雷迪思|author=陳怡妏|date=2017-11-28|newspaper=蘋果日報|accessdate=2018-01-01|archive-date=2020-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200606124533/https://tw.appledaily.com/international/daily/20171128/37858082|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年9月Meredith宣布將以1億9千萬美元將[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]賣給Salesforce.com的總裁Marc Benioff夫婦。

2019年5月31日，梅雷迪斯公司宣佈以1.1億美元出售[[運動畫刊|運動畫刊]]給Authentic Brands Group。

